unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)

-- Enable monster spawner.
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idMonsterSpawner) then
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idMonsterSpawner, false)
	end

end

function Start(idActorSpawned, idActorSpawner)

-- Enable a barrier and a rope.
	Hydra.ActorEnable(idBarrier)
	Hydra.Wait(2)
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idActorSpawned) then
		idRope = Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idChest, idActorSpawned, FX_ROPE, true)
	end

end

unk_9c63f9d.value:
-- Disable the barrier and turn off the rope.
	Hydra.ActorDisable(idBarrier)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffect(idChest, idRope)
